item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

MagicBean:

you guys im useing a hybrid pvp source and if you have used it before when you click the pking tele it gives you all the spots where you can pk at then if you click one of them it gives you a option to go to yanille or ardugone how do i change the teles for that?

You find the ID for the button you’re clicking, find the frame It’s sending, and edit the text. I’m going to take a wild guess and say that you’re using PI. Try looking for “ActionButtons”. If you’re wanting to change where the options take you, I’ll start you off. I believe one of the packet ID’s is 9158.
